> @ofrobots & @targos do you have any idea how the work you've done in nodejs/node#7016 might interact with the rest of Chromium?

Since the changes in nodejs/node#7016 are ABI-only, and API compatible, as long as Chromium is built from source along with the V8 + ABI changes, I think it should work.

